snippet.textDisplay: 🇵🇰❤ As a proud Pashtun from Peshawar, Pakistan, it fills me with joy to see this incredible masterpiece gaining recognition worldwide. Rehma, the talented American Pakistani singer from Los Angeles, brings such a refreshing vibe to this performance. It's amazing how she wasn't known in Pakistan before, but thanks to Coke Studio Pakistan's "Harkalay" song, she's finally getting the recognition she deserves. When I first heard her, I couldn't help but think of Camila Cabello – their resemblance is uncanny! But what really steals the show is Rehma's heartfelt connection to the lyrics. You can feel every emotion in her voice, like she's speaking directly to your soul. And let's not forget the male vocalist – his voice is pure magic! Together, they've created a masterpiece that transcends borders. This song is truly something special. 🌟

snippet.textDisplay:
Best CokeStudio Seasons and Best CokeStudio Producers are Rohail Hyatt and Xulfi so far. 

Rohail Hyatt aik alag level hai. Usko digest krna bhi har aik ke bas ki baat nhi. And Xulfi aik alag story hai. But beech me ko seasons aye wo although apni jaga achy thy but wo level ni rha tha jo Rohail Hyatt ka tha aur jo abi Xulfi ke production me hai. 
Rohail’s focus was on music maturity. His POV was music aisa ho ke jo music ki tameez rakhta hai wo impress hojaye. But Xulfi’s focus on eastern and western Music fusion with videography cuz ye aj ki audience ki demand hai. Music samjhna har aik ka kaam ni but video achi hogi to har aik accept krega. Plus Xulfi works on a bit modern style fusion. 

Well these 2 producers and and their seasons was/are epic. Hats off 🎩
